data.description: BUYER WALKTHROUGH Saturday, April 27th - 12 to 1PM, (Do not approach home before, and you must contact us to be added to the list for Saturday, see private remarks Agents!). Mansion on the Lake! Zillow value is $550k! Greer Elementary School (8/10) district. Welcome home to luxury living at 227 Edge Water Dr! This stunning mansion overlooking a beautiful lake is the epitome of elegance and comfort. With 4 full bedrooms, a bonus room that could easily be converted into a 5th bedroom, and multiple living spaces, there is room for everyone. The back yard is fenced and has a lovely pool perfect for this summer!   The spacious chef's kitchen features granite countertops, high-end appliances, and ample storage space. Hardwood floors throughout add warmth and charm to the home. Unwind and relax in the backyard oasis complete with a pool, perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors.  Located in a prime location with easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, this home offers the best of both worlds - a serene retreat while still being close to all the action.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a showing today! This property is being sold "as is." Prospective buyers are encouraged to perform all necessary inspections and evaluations prior to purchase. House is not  vacant!!! Do not use ShowingTime, Agent is ONLY transactional do not reach out to him, our info is in private remarks, Check out the really good 3D Matterport virtual tour! It shows you everything! Property Problem Solvers will help you solve your problem, for more details get in touch with us!
